cal check-up and treatment, social insurance, and working hours. In addition to regulations regarding contracts, there are stipulations regarding various fees to be collected during the migration cycle, including commission fees between enterprise and broker and service fees between worker and recruitment enterprise \u2014 both of which the worker is responsible for. Workers are also liable to pay a deposit for collateral security to the enterprise, in the event the worker violates his or her contract.641 Subsequent regulations, released by MoLISA, placed a cap on such fees\u2014for example, capping broker commissions at one month\u2019s salary per worker per year.642 Nevertheless, it is unclear how well such regulations are monitored; and Vietnamese workers, many of whom", "start_char_idx": null, "end_char_idx": null, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_seperator": "\n"}, "__type__": "1"}, "9bea1bcb-465e-48a3-9afc-36958f073117": {"__data__": {"id_": "9bea1bcb-465e-48a3-9afc-36958f073117", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/right-health-right-health-low-skilled-labour-migrants-asean-countries", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "The Right to Health: Right to Health for Low-Skilled Labour Migrants in ASEAN Countries", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/right-health-right-health-low-skilled-labour-migrants-asean-countries", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "53696a8c9cece325372654f7f31939d24195159cdafebf5d11129b341a3339d1"}, "3": {"node_id": "dd116b5e-c660-45a8-a1f5-7840b568577e", "node_type": null, "metadata":